{"tid":1056332,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"最恐懼的生日驚魂，來自香港的恐怖遊戲《牛一》","createTime":"2019-03-11T06:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T03:07:55.000Z","uid":99607,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5af4fe64c8be12acc1baaa2e81795b604e309996","tid":1056332,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TbFkSu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TbFkSu.jpg&h=e5f16e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《牛一》是一款解謎敘事類的遊戲，劇情描述女主角在生日時被男友綁架並軟禁在密室，玩家必須在房間裡找尋逃脫的線索，遊戲設計參考了很多港產鬼片和的駭人聽聞的真實案件，開發者也分享是受到赤燭《返校》的啟發，才開始嘗試創作具香港本土特色的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n屌  字太多唔撚Copy啦<br />\n第一眼睇落去 好撚似還願 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望唔好爛尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.incgmedia.com/index.php/say-gaming/ghostpie-birthday?fbclid=IwAR3oB3zg9TBjkFrJglf6vpmlZoygWMBFYlQ6fIgHyDwyZPhvEX-ozOTUZfI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.incgmedia.com%2Findex.php%2Fsay-gaming%2Fghostpie-birthday%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3oB3zg9TBjkFrJglf6vpmlZoygWMBFYlQ6fIgHyDwyZPhvEX-ozOTUZfI&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FB5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=17690fa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.incgmedia.com/index.php/say-gaming/ghostpie-birthday?fbclid=IwAR3oB3zg9TBjkFrJglf6vpmlZoygWMBFYlQ6fIgHyDwyZPhvEX-ozOTUZfI</a>"},{"pid":"c7687487298b4630027cddf76013927b3157f70a","tid":1056332,"uid":99607,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"九龍城寨 又加一分<br />\n所以話香港點可以無咗九龍城寨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212b052e0839ea46cd48143b726cdbc938c8ccc1","tid":1056332,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb2bc4a406baa6f3c2ffd10e